## SliverAppBar
SliverAppBar has flexible height and can auto-hides itself. The Sliver app bar is a material app bar that can scroll.
When it scrolls, it gives an effect of auto-hide.
It integrates with [CustomScrollView](https://docs.flutter.io/flutter/widgets/CustomScrollView-class.html)
to provide support for flexible height in AppBar.

***Target Audience:*** Beginner

***Recipe:*** Implementing SliverAppBar in Flutter for Android and iOS mobile apps.

***Focus Widget:*** [SliverAppBar](https://docs.flutter.io/flutter/material/SliverAppBar-class.html)

